metadata.name: BLeU WoRld
metadata.description:
There are endless possibilities in a BLeU WoRld. 

Huge shoutout to @0xTjo for the BLeU movement. The collector of this art will receive an airdrop of the piece 'endless possibilities' from my 1/1 collection, INTROSPECTION666. 

I'm NOOSH, a 22 year old student and self taught digital artist from Wales.
